        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Brisbane sellers can reduce valuation risk by running an auction campaign where buyers compete unconditionally, by ensuring the contract becomes unconditional before the buyer's finance deadline, and by pricing the property accurately so the sale price is well-supported by comparable sales evidence. An agent with a deep local sales record can provide comparable evidence that makes a low valuation less likely."
      }
